 * Write to syslog or/and some separate debug log
 * Pass usbfs device filename from udev
 * Have a table of supported VID:PID combinations and match devices
   against it
 * Use dbus(?) to communicate with frontends
 * (?) Add a target to build hald-addon and write hal rules
Frontends:
 1. Dump current link status (perfect for use with conky)
